            <fr:title text="Strong convexity">Strong convexity</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>A function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mu ]]></fr:tex>-strongly convex if and only if 
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[g(\boldsymbol {x}) = f(\boldsymbol {x}) - \frac {\mu }{2} ||\boldsymbol {x}||_2^2]]></fr:tex>
is convex, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\forall  \boldsymbol {x} \in  \mathrm {dom} f]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
